We've added support for Instagram! Now you can update your Blued Timeline automatically when you add a new post to your Instagram account. And also:

- Image Uploading speed greatly improved;
- Posts display quality optimisation; 
- Bring back nearby feed column;
- Various bug fixes and performance improvements.

Thanks for supporting the Blued Team：）
If you encounter any issue or require further assistance , contact us at support@blued.com
Or find us on Twitter: @Blued , Facebook: @Blued. We'll look into it thoroughly.

